The article is a statement issued on October 22, 2019, offering warm congratulations to the people of Japan on the occasion of the enthronement of the new Emperor and Empress. The statement highlights the strong bonds of friendship between the American and Japanese people and emphasizes the global partnership as a pillar of peace and prosperity in the Indo-Pacific region and the world. The statement also mentions the noble endeavor of advancing democracy, liberty, and human dignity for all. The message concludes by expressing fondest regards and utmost respect to the people of Japan on this auspicious and joyous occasion.